    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――そろそろ夏休みが終わる頃",
      "startTime": 56.4656927109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ゆゆしき事態です",
      "startTime": 58.7990288417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski002.wav",
      "text": "いえ、これは非常事態と言わざるを得ません",
      "startTime": 61.9551476161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かに私達はBIG4になり日々忙しいです",
      "startTime": 66.3365340869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski003.wav",
      "text": "夏休みに入ってからも、ありがたいことに仕事続き",
      "startTime": 71.4067504294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "時間を捻出するのにも苦労します",
      "startTime": 76.0383254687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski004.wav",
      "text": "だからと言って――",
      "startTime": 79.4884809494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski005.wav",
      "text": "なんでまだ誰も、夏休みの宿題が終わってないんですか",
      "startTime": 81.89170386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それは……仕事の反省会をしたり",
      "startTime": 86.8383248965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ktn002.wav",
      "text": "ライブの見直しをするのに時間使いたくて……",
      "startTime": 91.3000088374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんと宿題しようと思って誘うんだけど",
      "startTime": 95.0572585742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ngs002.wav",
      "text": "つい一緒に反省会しちゃって……",
      "startTime": 98.7333421707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "な、夏休みの宿題は、最終週に全て倒すべし！",
      "startTime": 102.2779837291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-suz002.wav",
      "text": "……が成宮家の家訓ですの",
      "startTime": 108.4000083923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ノート開くと眠くなっちゃうんだよね～",
      "startTime": 111.3904339473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-mei002.wav",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんは進んでるの？",
      "startTime": 115.5072566669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、もちろん終わらせていますよ",
      "startTime": 117.8237672806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski006.wav",
      "text": "七月中に、全部、余すところなく、完璧に",
      "startTime": 122.2405900002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-mei003.wav",
      "text": "おお～！",
      "startTime": 128.7786876679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もう、感心してる場合じゃありませんよ！",
      "startTime": 131.3425128937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski007.wav",
      "text": "夏休みの宿題は、勉強するだけが目的じゃありません",
      "startTime": 135.5000037511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "長期休暇の中で、与えられた課題を、自分で組んだ",
      "startTime": 139.9678071976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski008.wav",
      "text": "スケジュールに沿って期日までに終わらせる……",
      "startTime": 144.3666704178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういう、社会人として……アイドルという仕事を",
      "startTime": 147.6844215393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski009.wav",
      "text": "する上で必要な精神を学ぶことも重要なんです",
      "startTime": 151.5047151883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ましてや私達は今やBIG4の一角",
      "startTime": 155.7434235573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ski010.wav",
      "text": "その自覚をしっかりもって活動しなくては……",
      "startTime": 159.8380485217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "けど、仕事やレッスンは自分達のペースで",
      "startTime": 163.3742620468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-ktn004.wav",
      "text": "しっかりこなせているじゃない",
      "startTime": 166.5666704178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうですわ。沙季の言う精神はすでに学んでいる",
      "startTime": 168.8017447472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2509_01_01-suz004.wav",
      "text": "でしたら、何も問題ないのでは？",
